<s> This was an example of a member of the Imperial Family who abdicated and then returned and became the Emperor because there was no one to succeed the enthronement ; it is said that the event of Emperor Uda 's enthronement could have been set up by FUJIWARA no Yoshiko and Mototsune , although Imperial Prince Motoyoshi was still alive . </s>
